docTitle.name: shortTitle
docTitle.content: Mandatory Provident Fund Schemes (Appointment of Dates for Purposes of Section 19Y(3)) Notice

section.name: s2
section.heading: Appointment of dates for purposes of section 19Y(3) of the Ordinance

subsection.content: The date set out in column 3 of the Schedule opposite to a constituent fund of a registered scheme set out in column 2 of that Schedule is the day appointed for that constituent fund (relevant day).
The relevant day is appointed for the purposes of paragraph (a) of the definition of material day in section 19Y(3) of the Ordinance.
